Class Ocean

java.lang.Object
  Ocean

public class Ocean
extends java.lang.Object

Represent an ocean of the given dimensions. The ocean stores an array of squares that hold fish rocks etc... The ocean is used to deliver information about its ocean squares and pass data onto them.

Author:
Matthew Maglennon
